    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "data": {
        "text": "Imala kee tolfadhu. Amantii jechuun hawaasa jiran keessatti kan jiraatamudha. Imala Tokkoffaa akkuma xumurteen, dubbisa Macaafa Qulqulluu barbaadde yeroo dubbistu qabxiileen si gargaaruu danda'an kunooti."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "sectionMarker",
      "data": {
        "theme": "sharing-life",
        "title": "Qoodi",
        "icon": "sharing-life"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "data": {
        "style": "ordered",
        "items": [
          "Torbee kana Waaqayyo wajjin akkamitti dabarsite?",
          "Waanti akka galateeffattu si godhan maalinni?",
          "Waaqayyo maal akka si gargaaru barbaaddaa?",
          "Wanta si barbaachisu keessatti akkamitti si gargaaruu dandeenya?",
          "Walii walii keessaniif kadhadhaa"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "notesArea",
      "data": {
        "notes": "",
        "storageKey": "note"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "sectionMarker",
      "data": {
        "theme": "review",
        "title": "Keessa Deebii",
        "icon": "review"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "data": {
        "style": "ordered",
        "items": [
          "Erga walga'ii keenya yeroo darbeeti maal maal shaakalte?",
          "Namootni ati kunuunsaa jirtuu akkam? Maaltu baay'ee isaan gargaara?",
          "Shaakala Waaqayyoo namootaaf hiruu dandeesseetta? Isaan wajjin kadhatteetta?",
          "Namoota sanaaf kadhadhu"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "notesArea",
      "data": {
        "notes": "",
        "storageKey": "note"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "sectionMarker",
      "data": {
        "theme": "bible-study",
        "title": "Dubbisi",
        "icon": "bible-study"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "data": {
        "style": "ordered",
        "items": [
          "Dubbisicha sagalee olkaasii al-lama dubbisi",
          "Gargaarsa garichaatiin namni tokko dubbisicha jecha mataa isaatiin akka himuu godhaa",
          "Waanti haaraan dabalame yookiin hir'ate jira?"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "data": {
        "text": "Dubbisa Macaafa Qulqulluu Filadhu<br>"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "notesArea",
      "data": {
        "notes": "",
        "storageKey": "note"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "sectionMarker",
      "data": {
        "theme": "bible-study",
        "title": "Gargar baafadhu",
        "icon": "bible-study"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "data": {
        "style": "ordered",
        "items": [
          "Dubbisni kun si'iif maal bakka bu'a?",
          "Dubbisa kana keessaa wanti jaallatte yookiin si jeeqe maalidha?",
          "Dubbisni kun waa'ee Waaqayyoo fi waa'ee namootaa maal sitti hima?"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "notesArea",
